        "subject": "LU-9715 libcfs: crash in cpu_pattern parsing code",
        "message": "LU-9715 libcfs: crash in cpu_pattern parsing code\n\nThe for loop in cfs_cpt_table_create_pattern() that scans\nfor brackets to count the number of cpts is broken.\nIt will increment bracket beyond NULL and it will increment ncpt\nbeyond the number of available cpts. This has been fixed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I87bc9de4c531c42c421e8e62edd881417dbb242d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
